{"tid":1362631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理優round] [技術文] 如何推鳩何妖上律師紀律審裁組","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:05:40.000Z","uid":288821,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc5dd2385bc36712dd7fd76dfc4b57448a6ee45","tid":1362631,"uid":288821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"大狀朋友助攻無account<br />\n推上熱門🔫🔫🔫🔫🔫<br />\n尋晚po咗《政事台》但有巴打教路話《時事台》較適合<br />\n**********<br />\n尋晚發夢嘅時候寫咗封信 port 鳩何妖上律師會～<br />\n今朝起身嘅時候一個唔小心默撚低咗，供各巴打抄考指教～<br />\n上載咗範文檔，想修改可以編輯 word 檔，如果覺得唔洗編輯都啱洗嘅，直接印 PDF 簽個名+日期，填埋律師會張 complaint form 可以即刻用。<br />\n香港律師會執業操守組投訴表格：<a href=\"http://www.hklawsoc.org.hk/pub_c/conduct/complaint.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklawsoc.org.hk%2Fpub_c%2Fconduct%2Fcomplaint.asp&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=27240765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklawsoc.org.hk/pub_c/conduct/complaint.asp</a><br />\nWord 檔：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qIbkZV0T8TBLaaQCD9V0FPJhG4yDnra4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qIbkZV0T8TBLaaQCD9V0FPJhG4yDnra4&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=7a88664b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qIbkZV0T8TBLaaQCD9V0FPJhG4yDnra4</a><br />\nPDF 檔：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=16WGevcKxWor4T7b4qhvvi5jMTS1Jutim\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D16WGevcKxWor4T7b4qhvvi5jMTS1Jutim&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f632c6f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=16WGevcKxWor4T7b4qhvvi5jMTS1Jutim</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjxdgpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjxdgpQ.jpg&h=8d52f10b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CvVuKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb